his wish to end the destructive power of the Elder Wand at the end. This collection of essays on alchemical symbolism and transformations in Rowling's series demonstrates how Harry's work with magical objects, people, and creatures transfigure desire, power, and identity. As Harry's leaden existence on Privet Drive is transformed in the company of his friends and teachers, the Harry Potter novels have transformed millions of readers, inspiring us to find the gold in our ordinary lives.","industryIdentifiers":[{"type":"ISBN_13","identifier":"9781476681344"},{"type":"ISBN_10","identifier":"1476681341"}],"readingModes":{"text":false,"image":true},"pageCount":323,"printType":"BOOK","categories":["Literary Criticism"],"maturityRating":"NOT_MATURE","allowAnonLogging":false,"contentVersion":"preview-1.0.0","panelizationSummary":{"containsEpubBubbles":false,"containsImageBubbles":false},"imageLinks":{"smallThumbnail":"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=8fcQEAAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=5&edge=curl&source=gbs_api","thumbnail":"http://books.google.com/books/content?id=8fcQEAAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api"},"language":"en","previewLink":"http://books.google.com.ua/books?id=8fcQEAAAQBAJ&pg=PA44&dq=harry+Potter&hl=&cd=31&source=gbs_api","infoLink":"http://books.google.com.ua/books?id=8fcQEAAAQBAJ&dq=harry+Potter&hl=&source=gbs_api","canonicalVolumeLink":"https://books.google.com/books/about/The_Alchemical_Harry_Potter.html?hl=&id=8fcQEAAAQBAJ"},"saleInfo":{"country":"UA","saleability":"NOT_FOR_SALE","isEbook":false},"accessInfo":{"country":"UA","viewability":"PARTIAL","embeddable":true,"publicDomain":false,"textToSpeechPermission":"ALLOWED","epub":{"isAvailable":false},"pdf":{"isAvailable":false},"webReaderLink":"http://play.google.com/books/reader?id=8fcQEAAAQBAJ&hl=&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_api","accessViewStatus":"SAMPLE","quoteSharingAllowed":false},"searchInfo":{"textSnippet":"SUNY, 1996. Granger, John. The Deathly Hal